<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="i-beg-your-pardon">I beg your pardon</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-beg-pardon-pardon">1.★ <strong>[未听清对方的话，请求重复；常简化为 “beg pardon” 或 “pardon”] 什么；请再说一遍：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— You’re very quiet today. 
你今天话很少啊。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Pardon? 
什么？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I said you’re very quiet today. 
我说你今天话很少。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[表示道歉] 对不起；请原谅：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I beg your pardon. I didn’t know this was your seat.
对不起，我不知道这座位是你的。</p></div></div>